@document.meta
title: Paru Bootstrap
description: Hook script that installs the paru AUR helper before chezmoi reads source state
authors: primary_desktop
categories: Package Management Bootstrap
tangle: ../../bootstrap-paru.sh
created: 2026-02-25
updated: 2026-02-25
version: 0.1.0
